<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Rust on Graplo</title><link>https://graplo.github.io/tags/rust/</link><description>Recent content in Rust on Graplo</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>es</language><managingEditor>graplo@disroot.com (Graplo)</managingEditor><webMaster>graplo@disroot.com (Graplo)</webMaster><copyright>© 2026 Graplo</copyright><lastBuildDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 19:51:38 -0500</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://graplo.github.io/tags/rust/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Cargo: instalar y gestionar programas escritos en Rust</title><link>https://graplo.github.io/blog/rust-bases-comandos/</link><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 19:51:38 -0500</pubDate><author>graplo@disroot.com (Graplo)</author><guid>https://graplo.github.io/blog/rust-bases-comandos/</guid><description>Cargo es el gestor de paquetes de Rust. Con él podés instalar programas de la comunidad directamente desde crates.io, sin repositorios ni PPAs.</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://graplo.github.io/blog/rust-bases-comandos/feature.webp"/></item><item><title>Helix - Salto De Linea</title><link>https://graplo.github.io/blog/helix-salto-de-linea/</link><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 23:36:16 -0500</pubDate><author>graplo@disroot.com (Graplo)</author><guid>https://graplo.github.io/blog/helix-salto-de-linea/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Helix es un editor de texto modal y moderno para terminal, escrito en Rust, diseñado para ser rápido y eficiente.&lt;/p&gt;</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://graplo.github.io/blog/helix-salto-de-linea/feature.webp"/></item><item><title>rmpc - instalación</title><link>https://graplo.github.io/blog/rmpc-installation/</link><pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>graplo@disroot.com (Graplo)</author><guid>https://graplo.github.io/blog/rmpc-installation/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="relative inline-block align-text-bottom icon"&gt;&lt;svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"&gt;&lt;path fill="currentColor" d="M511.1 367.1c0 44.18-42.98 80-95.1 80s-95.1-35.82-95.1-79.1c0-44.18 42.98-79.1 95.1-79.1c11.28 0 21.95 1.92 32.01 4.898V148.1L192 224l-.0023 208.1C191.1 476.2 149 512 95.1 512S0 476.2 0 432c0-44.18 42.98-79.1 95.1-79.1c11.28 0 21.95 1.92 32 4.898V126.5c0-12.97 10.06-26.63 22.41-30.52l319.1-94.49C472.1 .6615 477.3 0 480 0c17.66 0 31.97 14.34 32 31.99L511.1 367.1z"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/span&gt; Rmpc es un cliente moderno y rápido para Music Player Daemon (MPD). Escrito en Rust, está diseñado para funcionar en la terminal (TUI) de sistemas Linux. Se caracteriza por ser altamente configurable, tener soporte para carátulas de álbumes y ofrecer una experiencia de navegación de tres columnas tipo ranger.&lt;/p&gt;</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://graplo.github.io/blog/rmpc-installation/feature.webp"/></item><item><title>bat - Dracula Theme</title><link>https://graplo.github.io/blog/bat-dracula-theme/</link><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>graplo@disroot.com (Graplo)</author><guid>https://graplo.github.io/blog/bat-dracula-theme/</guid><description>&lt;h2 class="relative group"&gt;Puedes ver los temas disponibles con:
 &lt;div id="puedes-ver-los-temas-disponibles-con" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#puedes-ver-los-temas-disponibles-con" aria-label="Ancla"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight-wrapper"&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; bat --list-themes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h2 class="relative group"&gt;Y probar uno específico: En mi caso dracula
 &lt;div id="y-probar-uno-específico-en-mi-caso-dracula" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#y-probar-uno-espec%c3%adfico-en-mi-caso-dracula" aria-label="Ancla"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight-wrapper"&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; bat --theme&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#34;Dracula&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; ~/.config/fish/config.fish&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h2 class="relative group"&gt;Para hacerlo permanete lo ponemos &lt;code&gt;~/.config/fish/config.fish&lt;/code&gt;
 &lt;div id="para-hacerlo-permanete-lo-ponemos-configfishconfigfish" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#para-hacerlo-permanete-lo-ponemos-configfishconfigfish" aria-label="Ancla"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight-wrapper"&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;set&lt;/span&gt; -Ux BAT_THEME Dracula&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h2 class="relative group"&gt;Para saber cual theme esta en el momento
 &lt;div id="para-saber-cual-theme-esta-en-el-momento" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#para-saber-cual-theme-esta-en-el-momento" aria-label="Ancla"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight-wrapper"&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nv"&gt;$BAT_THEME&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://graplo.github.io/blog/bat-dracula-theme/feature.webp"/></item></channel></rss>